{"tid":2421522,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蓋茨不看好比特幣 籲投資者小心","createTime":"2021-02-24T14:16:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T16:14:43.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"48658b23207556713ff4aec7cf87e344f71ef5fc","tid":2421522,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T14:16:25.000Z","msg":"&lt;匯港通訊&gt; 虛擬貨幣比特幣(Bitcoin)近日持續創新高，一度衝破5.8萬美元創新高，但其後急回。微軟創辦人蓋茨(Bill Gates)接受外電訪問時表示，並不看好比特幣，他本人並不支持比特幣，因開採比特幣會消耗大量能源，破境環境。<br />\n<br />\n對於特斯拉(Tesla)創辦人馬斯克(Elon Musk)早前唱好比特幣，蓋茨認為，馬斯克擁有大量資金，非常老練，因此不擔心對方的比特幣會隨機漲跌，但那些在比特幣熱潮中買入的投資者，他們可能沒有那麼多閒錢，應該小心一些。<br />\n<br />\n根據Coindesk報價，比特幣最新報51880美元，跌8.31%。 (ST)"},{"pid":"4edfc1c6efbead0710ddd66ed74c7968643a0932","tid":2421522,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T14:59:05.000Z","msg":"挖礦真係好撚 ON 9<br />\n邊條冚家鏟諗出諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4533fb156106736b6692ea8c18670883488525f3","tid":2421522,"uid":213607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T15:00:34.000Z","msg":"為全球暖化出一分力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7b4bc2d59e42227348cad9d86a786b3299afac6","tid":2421522,"uid":211603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T15:03:40.000Z","msg":"我不看好蓋茨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a48d4e25e36e88d3ce3176293d4cfb4318624861","tid":2421522,"uid":226466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T15:03:42.000Z","msg":"央行不停印錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b1052d23b319fd61f57510286433439257018c0","tid":2421522,"uid":516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T15:08:54.000Z","msg":"淘金夠污染啦"},{"pid":"8a6d3dfe68e7b5a46a320924b0a81586fc6fe0c5","tid":2421522,"uid":15815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a48d4e25e36e88d3ce3176293d4cfb4318624861","tid":242152